<br />\n其實我都冇心情洗錢<br />\n<br />\n22:52熄燈 元朗警員離開 進入無警時份"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:24:44.000Z","msg":"仲要繼續撳錢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n重申七一宣言，設立死線，立即實行雙普選<br />\n<br />\n唔係仇警，大家一定要清楚知道點解要清算警隊。警暴（濫捕、濫告、不依法規）係暴政一部分，唔全面改革警隊、監警制度，只會令目前同將來爭取雙普選更加舉步維艱<br />\n<br />\n所以，絕對唔需要否認自己係針對警隊，針對警隊就係對準政權。唔通你淨係針對林鄭、唔針對政制，就會有雙普選？<br />\n<br />\n#五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n#唔撤就罷<br />\n#罷工罷巿罷買罷課<br />\n#我係香港人<br />\n#我參與全港四罷<br />\n#各區集會<br />\n#出核彈麻包袋都唔割蓆<br />\n#直至政府跪低<br />\n#解散警隊<br />\n#永遠不光顧荃灣北角元朗商戶<br />\n#抵制一切紅媒相關商業活動"},{"pid":"499866a0921ea2f81432408e9703225d181b0c00","tid":1488012,"uid":91230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:24:51.000Z","msg":"返工搭車罷唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n帶飯唔出街食減少消費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8db049cad10dbfbd173e398e46af98c0ea8f96ea","tid":1488012,"uid":229835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"499866a0921ea2f81432408e9703225d181b0c00","tid":1488012,"uid":91230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:24:51.000Z","msg":"返工搭車罷唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n帶飯唔出街食減少消費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:29:14.000Z","msg":"基本出入就梗係要啦<br />\n<br />\n你諗諗721班元朗既市民<br />\n<br />\n你仲有買野既意慾?"},{"pid":"a5d2293cc7974762b3abe48bc5f29aa78f0f4aec","tid":1488012,"uid":101498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:32:12.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">721晚 元朗站靜坐</span></span></strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WzsDUMG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWzsDUMG.jpg&h=f12e94e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmo